backup SLA			bind master				bind slave			mysql			influxdb

- Coverage/Commands		/etc/bind containging dns db;		/var/lib/bind;			mysqldump "db";		influx backup -database "db" /path


- RPO				acceptable data loss is the amount that will not hinder the function of the recovered service;


- Versioning			full each week, incr each day;


- Retention			kept for 1 month;


- Usability			recovery verified when service is back to functional state with data intact;


- Restoration criteria		should be restored when the data stored is compromised or erased;


- RTO				depends on the size of the db; however, it's just 1 command;


